<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>PC Building – Devon Shunn</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Share+Tech+Mono&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<script src="nav.js"></script>

<style>
:root{
  --bg:#070A12;
  --glass:rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  --glass2:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
  --border:rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
  --text:#fff;
  --muted:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
  --blue:#38bdf8;
  --purple:#a855f7;
  --accent:#e2e8f0;
  --accent2:#94a3b8;
  --accentglow:rgba(226,232,240,0.35);
  --dim:rgba(226,232,240,0.45);
}

*{ margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; font-family:Poppins,sans-serif; }
body{ background:var(--bg); color:var(--text); overflow-x:hidden; }
body::before{
  content:''; position:fixed; inset:0;
  background:repeating-linear-gradient(0deg,transparent,transparent 2px,rgba(0,0,0,0.025) 2px,rgba(0,0,0,0.025) 4px);
  pointer-events:none; z-index:999;
}

/* NAV */
header{ position:fixed; top:0; width:100%; backdrop-filter:blur(14px); background:rgba(7,10,18,0.85); border-bottom:1px solid var(--border); z-index:200; }
nav{ max-width:1100px; margin:auto; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; padding:14px 24px; }
nav ul{ display:flex; gap:26px; list-style:none; align-items:center; }
.nav-link{ color:var(--muted); text-decoration:none; transition:0.2s ease; }
.nav-link:hover{ color:var(--blue); }
.logo img{ height:42px; cursor:pointer; transition:0.25s ease; }
.logo img:hover{ transform:scale(1.05); filter:drop-shadow(0 0 12px rgba(56,189,248,0.6)); }
.nav-item{ position:relative; }
.dropdown{ position:absolute; top:100%; left:0; padding-top:12px; min-width:200px; background:transparent; display:flex; flex-direction:column; opacity:0; transform:translateY(6px); pointer-events:none; transition:0.25s ease; }
.dropdown-inner{ background:rgba(7,10,18,0.85); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:12px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; overflow:hidden; backdrop-filter:blur(14px); }
.dropdown a{ padding:10px 14px; text-decoration:none; color:var(--muted); font-size:14px; transition:0.2s ease; }
.dropdown a:hover{ background:rgba(56,189,248,0.12); color:var(--blue); }
.nav-item:hover .dropdown{ opacity:1; transform:translateY(0); pointer-events:auto; }

/* ---- HERO ---- */
.hero{ position:relative; min-height:100vh; display:flex; align-items:flex-end; overflow:hidden; }
.hero-bg{ position:absolute; inset:0; background:linear-gradient(180deg,#0a0c10 0%,#080a0f 35%,#070810 65%,#070A12 100%); }

.hero-sweep{ position:absolute; inset:0; overflow:hidden; pointer-events:none; }
.hero-sweep::before{
  content:''; position:absolute; top:-20%; left:-60%; width:40%; height:140%;
  background:linear-gradient(105deg,transparent 0%,rgba(226,232,240,0.015) 30%,rgba(226,232,240,0.05) 50%,rgba(226,232,240,0.015) 70%,transparent 100%);
  animation:sweepMove 9s ease-in-out infinite;
}
.hero-sweep::after{
  content:''; position:absolute; top:-20%; left:-60%; width:20%; height:140%;
  background:linear-gradient(105deg,transparent 0%,rgba(226,232,240,0.02) 50%,transparent 100%);
  animation:sweepMove 9s ease-in-out infinite 1.4s;
}
@keyframes sweepMove{ 0%{left:-60%} 100%{left:130%} }

.hero-grid{
  position:absolute; inset:0;
  background-image:
    linear-gradient(rgba(226,232,240,0.05) 1px,transparent 1px),
    linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(226,232,240,0.04) 1px,transparent 1px);
  background-size:55px 55px;
  transform:perspective(700px) rotateX(54deg) translateY(28%);
  transform-origin:bottom center;
  animation:gridPulse 5s ease-in-out infinite;
}
@keyframes gridPulse{ 0%,100%{opacity:0.7} 50%{opacity:1} }

.hero-dots{ position:absolute; inset:0; pointer-events:none; overflow:hidden; }
.hero-dots span{ position:absolute; border-radius:50%; background:var(--accent); animation:dotFloat linear infinite; opacity:0; }
@keyframes dotFloat{ 0%{opacity:0;transform:translateY(0)} 20%{opacity:0.5} 80%{opacity:0.15} 100%{opacity:0;transform:translateY(-70px)} }

.hero-glow{ position:absolute; bottom:12%; left:50%; transform:translateX(-50%); width:900px; height:300px; background:radial-gradient(ellipse,rgba(148,163,184,0.14) 0%,rgba(226,232,240,0.06) 45%,transparent 70%); filter:blur(50px); pointer-events:none; }
.hero-img-wrap{ position:absolute; inset:0; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; }
.hero-img-wrap img{ width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover; opacity:0.45; mix-blend-mode:lighten; }

.hero-content{ position:relative; z-index:2; max-width:1100px; margin:0 auto; padding:0 24px 80px; width:100%; }
.breadcrumb{ display:flex; align-items:center; gap:8px; margin-bottom:24px; font-family:'Share Tech Mono',monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4); letter-spacing:1px; }
.breadcrumb a{ color:var(--accent); text-decoration:none; }
.breadcrumb a:hover{ text-decoration:underline; }
.hero-tag{ font-family:'Share Tech Mono',monospace; font-size:12px; letter-spacing:3px; color:var(--accent); margin-bottom:16px; opacity:0.9; }
.hero-title{ font-size:clamp(40px,7vw,82px); line-height:0.95; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:-2px; margin-bottom:22px; }
.hero-title .line2{ color:transparent; -webkit-text-stroke:1px rgba(226,232,240,0.45); }
.hero-sub{ color:var(--muted); max-width:580px; line-height:1.8; font-size:16px; margin-bottom:36px; }
.hero-meta{ display:flex; gap:32px; flex-wrap:wrap; }
.meta-item{ display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:4px; }
.meta-label{ font-family:'Share Tech Mono',monospace; font-size:10px; letter-spacing:2px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35); text-transform:uppercase; }
.meta-value{ font-size:14px; color:var(--accent); font-weight:600; }
.scroll-hint{ position:absolute; bottom:30px; right:40px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; gap:8px; opacity:0.4; animation:bounce 2s ease-in-out infinite; }
@keyframes bounce{ 0%,100%{transform:translateY(0)} 50%{transform:translateY(6px)} }
.scroll-hint span{ font-family:'Share Tech Mono',monospace; font-size:10px; letter-spacing:2px; color:var(--accent); }
.scroll-arrow{ width:1px; height:40px; background:linear-gradient(to bottom,var(--accent),transparent); }

/* ---- MAIN ---- */
main{ max-width:1100px; margin:0 auto; padding:0 24px 120px; }
.section-label{ font-family:'Share Tech Mono',monospace; font-size:11px; letter-spacing:3px; color:var(--accent); opacity:0.7; margin-bottom:12px; display:block; }
.fade{ opacity:0; transform:translateY(30px); transition:0.9s ease; }
.fade.show{ opacity:1; transform:translateY(0); }
.back-link{ display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:8px; color:var(--muted); text-decoration:none; font-size:14px; transition:0.2s ease; margin-bottom:60px; padding-top:40px; font-family:'Share Tech Mono',monospace; letter-spacing:1px; }
.back-link:hover{ color:var(--accent); }

/* ---- INTRO ---- */
.intro-block{ padding:80px 0 60px; display:grid; grid-template-columns:1.2fr 1fr; gap:80px; align-items:start; border-bottom:1px solid var(--border); }
.intro-block h2{ font-size:38px; line-height:1.2; margin-bottom:20px; }
.intro-block p{ color:var(--muted); line-height:1.9; font-size:15px; margin-bottom:16px; }
.intro-block em{ color:rgba(255,255,255,0.92); font-style:normal; }
.stat-stack{ display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:20px; }
.stat-card{ background:var(--glass); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:16px; padding:20px 24px; backdrop-filter:blur(8px); position:relative; overflow:hidden; }
.stat-card::before{ content:''; position:absolute; top:0; left:0; width:3px; height:100%; background:linear-gradient(to bottom,var(--accent),var(--purple)); border-radius:3px 0 0 3px; }
.stat-card .num{ font-size:28px; font-weight:700; color:var(--accent); line-height:1; font-family:'Share Tech Mono',monospace; }
.stat-card .desc{ font-size:13px; color:var(--muted); margin-top:5px; }

/* ---- ERA TIMELINE ---- */
.era-section{ padding:80px 0; border-bottom:1px solid var(--border); }
.era-section > h2{ font-size:34px; margin-bottom:12px; }
.era-section > .lead{ color:var(--muted); max-width:680px; line-height:1.8; margin-bottom:64px; }

.era-track{ display:flex; flex-direction:column; position:relative; }
.era-track::before{
  content:''; position:absolute; left:28px; top:0; bottom:0; width:2px;
  background:linear-gradient(to bottom,var(--accent),var(--purple),transparent);
  opacity:0.25;
}

.era-block{ display:grid; grid-template-columns:72px 1fr; padding:0 0 72px; }
.era-block:last-child{ padding-bottom:0; }
.era-dot-col{ display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; padding-top:5px; }
.era-dot{ width:18px; height:18px; border-radius:50%; background:var(--bg); flex-shrink:0; position:relative; z-index:1; border:2px solid rgba(226,232,240,0.25); }
.era-dot.glow{ border-color:var(--accent); background:rgba(226,232,240,0.08); box-shadow:0 0 18px var(--accentglow); }
.era-dot.upcoming{ border-color:rgba(168,85,247,0.4); background:rgba(168,85,247,0.06); animation:upcomingPulse 2s ease-in-out infinite; }
@keyframes upcomingPulse{ 0%,100%{box-shadow:0 0 8px rgba(168,85,247,0.3)} 50%{box-shadow:0 0 22px rgba(168,85,247,0.6)} }

.era-body{ padding-left:24px; }
.era-kicker{ font-family:'Share Tech Mono',monospace; font-size:11px; letter-spacing:2px; color:var(--dim); margin-bottom:6px; display:block; }
.era-kicker.bright{ color:var(--accent); }
.era-kicker.k-upcoming{ color:rgba(168,85,247,0.8); }
.era-body h3{ font-size:26px; margin-bottom:12px; line-height:1.2; }
.era-body > p{ color:var(--muted); line-height:1.9; font-size:15px; max-width:720px; margin-bottom:22px; }

/* Callout box */
.callout-box{
  background:rgba(226,232,240,0.04); border:1px solid rgba(226,232,240,0.13);
  border-radius:14px; padding:20px 24px; margin-bottom:24px; position:relative; overflow:hidden;
}
.callout-box::before{ content:''; position:absolute; top:0; left:0; right:0; height:2px; background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,var(--accent),transparent); }
.callout-box p{ color:var(--muted); font-size:14px; line-height:1.8; margin:0; }
.callout-box strong{ color:var(--accent); font-weight:600; }

/* Spec table */
.spec-table{ background:var(--glass2); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:16px; overflow:hidden; margin-bottom:24px; }
.spec-table-header{ padding:12px 20px; background:rgba(226,232,240,0.04); border-bottom:1px solid var(--border); font-family:'Share Tech Mono',monospace; font-size:11px; letter-spacing:2px; color:var(--dim); }
.spec-row-item{ display:grid; grid-template-columns:160px 1fr; padding:11px 20px; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05); font-size:14px; }
.spec-row-item:last-child{ border-bottom:none; }
.skey{ font-family:'Share Tech Mono',monospace; font-size:12px; color:rgba(226,232,240,0.4); letter-spacing:0.5px; padding-top:1px; }
.sval{ color:var(--text); font-weight:500; }

/* Photo row */
.photo-row{ display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr; gap:12px; margin-bottom:24px; }
.photo-cell-sm{ border-radius:12px; overflow:hidden; border:1px solid var(--border); background:var(--glass2); position:relative; }
.photo-cell-sm img{ width:100%; height:160px; object-fit:cover; display:block; transition:transform 0.4s ease; }
.photo-cell-sm:hover img{ transform:scale(1.05); }
.ph-sm-placeholder{ width:100%; height:160px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-size:28px; opacity:0.12; background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(226,232,240,0.04),rgba(148,163,184,0.03)); }
.ph-sm-cap{ position:absolute; bottom:0; left:0; right:0; padding:14px 10px 8px; background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(0,0,0,0.8),transparent); font-size:10px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7); opacity:0; transition:0.3s ease; font-family:'Share Tech Mono',monospace; letter-spacing:1px; }
.photo-cell-sm:hover .ph-sm-cap{ opacity:1; }

/* Pills */
.era-pills{ display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:7px; margin-top:20px; }
.era-pill{ padding:4px 12px; border-radius:999px; font-family:'Share Tech Mono',monospace; font-size:10px; letter-spacing:0.5px; border:1px solid rgba(226,232,240,0.18); color:rgba(226,232,240,0.7); background:rgba(226,232,240,0.04); }
.era-pill.p-upcoming{ border-color:rgba(168,85,247,0.25); color:rgba(168,85,247,0.8); background:rgba(168,85,247,0.05); }

/* Upcoming banner */
.upcoming-banner{ display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:8px; padding:5px 14px; border-radius:999px; border:1px solid rgba(168,85,247,0.3); background:rgba(168,85,247,0.07); font-family:'Share Tech Mono',monospace; font-size:11px; color:rgba(168,85,247,0.85); margin-bottom:12px; }

/* ---- OMEN FEATURE CARD ---- */
.omen-card{
  margin:40px 0;
  background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(226,232,240,0.05),rgba(148,163,184,0.03));
  border:1px solid rgba(226,232,240,0.18);
  border-radius:22px; padding:40px;
  position:relative; overflow:hidden;
  display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 300px; gap:48px; align-items:start;
}
.omen-card::before{ content:''; position:absolute; top:0; left:0; right:0; height:2px; background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,var(--accent),rgba(168,85,247,0.5),transparent); }
.omen-card h3{ font-size:26px; margin-bottom:10px; }
.omen-card .omen-body > p{ color:var(--muted); font-size:15px; line-height:1.8; margin-bottom:20px; }

.omen-specs-list{ display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:0; }
.omen-spec{ display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:3px; padding:12px 0; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06); }
.omen-spec:last-child{ border-bottom:none; }
.omen-spec-key{ font-family:'Share Tech Mono',monospace; font-size:10px; letter-spacing:2px; color:rgba(226,232,240,0.38); }
.omen-spec-val{ font-size:14px; color:var(--accent); font-weight:600; }
.omen-spec-sub{ font-size:12px; color:var(--muted); }

/* ---- SKILLS ---- */
.skills-section{ padding:80px 0; border-bottom:1px solid var(--border); }
.skills-section h2{ font-size:34px; margin-bottom:12px; }
.skills-section .lead{ color:var(--muted); max-width:680px; line-height:1.8; margin-bottom:56px; }
.skills-grid{ display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:20px; }
.skill-card{ background:var(--glass); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:20px; padding:28px; backdrop-filter:blur(8px); transition:border-color 0.3s ease,background 0.3s ease; position:relative; overflow:hidden; }
.skill-card::after{ content:''; position:absolute; inset:0; border-radius:20px; background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(226,232,240,0.03),transparent 60%); pointer-events:none; }
.skill-card:hover{ border-color:rgba(226,232,240,0.22); background:rgba(255,255,255,0.07); }
.skill-num{ font-family:'Share Tech Mono',monospace; font-size:38px; font-weight:700; color:rgba(226,232,240,0.08); line-height:1; margin-bottom:12px; }
.skill-card h3{ font-size:18px; margin-bottom:10px; }
.skill-card p{ color:var(--muted); font-size:14px; line-height:1.8; }
.tech-row{ display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:8px; margin-top:14px; }
.tech-pill{ padding:4px 12px; border-radius:999px; font-family:'Share Tech Mono',monospace; font-size:11px; border:1px solid rgba(226,232,240,0.2); color:var(--accent); background:rgba(226,232,240,0.04); }

/* ---- GALLERY ---- */
.photo-section{ padding:80px 0; border-bottom:1px solid var(--border); }
.photo-section h2{ font-size:34px; margin-bottom:12px; }
.photo-section .lead{ color:var(--muted); max-width:600px; line-height:1.8; margin-bottom:48px; }
.photo-grid{ display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr; gap:16px; }
.photo-cell{ border-radius:16px; overflow:hidden; border:1px solid var(--border); background:var(--glass2); position:relative; cursor:pointer; }
.photo-cell img{ width:100%; height:100%; min-height:190px; object-fit:cover; display:block; transition:transform 0.5s ease; }
.photo-cell:hover img{ transform:scale(1.05); }
.photo-cell.tall{ grid-row:span 2; }
.photo-cell.wide{ grid-column:span 2; }
.photo-caption{ position:absolute; bottom:0; left:0; right:0; padding:20px 14px 12px; background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(0,0,0,0.85),transparent); font-size:11px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8); opacity:0; transition:0.3s ease; font-family:'Share Tech Mono',monospace; letter-spacing:1px; }
.photo-cell:hover .photo-caption{ opacity:1; }
.photo-placeholder{ width:100%; min-height:190px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; justify-content:center; gap:10px; background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(226,232,240,0.03),rgba(148,163,184,0.03)); color:rgba(255,255,255,0.13); font-size:12px; font-family:'Share Tech Mono',monospace; }
.photo-placeholder .icon{ font-size:26px; opacity:0.2; }

/* ---- PROGRESS ---- */
.progress-section{ padding:80px 0; display:grid; grid-template-columns:1.1fr 1fr; gap:80px; align-items:start; }
.progress-section h2{ font-size:34px; margin-bottom:20px; }
.progress-section p{ color:var(--muted); line-height:1.9; font-size:15px; margin-bottom:16px; }
.bars-list{ display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:16px; }
.bar-row{ display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:6px; }
.bar-label{ display:flex; justify-content:space-between; font-size:13px; color:var(--muted); }
.bar-label span:last-child{ color:var(--accent); font-family:'Share Tech Mono',monospace; }
.bar-track{ height:5px; background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border-radius:5px; overflow:hidden; }
.bar-fill{ height:100%; border-radius:5px; background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--accent),var(--purple)); width:0%; transition:width 1.3s ease; }

footer{ text-align:center; padding:60px 20px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5); border-top:1px solid var(--border); }

/* ---- RESPONSIVE ---- */
@media(max-width:900px){
  .intro-block,.progress-section{ grid-template-columns:1fr; gap:40px; }
  .skills-grid{ grid-template-columns:1fr; }
  .photo-row{ grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; }
  .photo-grid{ grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; }
  .omen-card{ grid-template-columns:1fr; gap:32px; }
  .hero-title{ font-size:44px; }
}
@media(max-width:600px){
  .photo-grid{ grid-template-columns:1fr; }
  .photo-cell.tall,.photo-cell.wide{ grid-column:span 1; grid-row:span 1; }
  .photo-row{ grid-template-columns:1fr; }
  .hero-meta{ gap:20px; }
  .era-track::before{ left:20px; }
  .era-block{ grid-template-columns:56px 1fr; }
  .spec-row-item{ grid-template-columns:1fr; gap:2px; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg"></div>
  <div class="hero-sweep"></div>
  <div class="hero-grid"></div>
  <div class="hero-glow"></div>
  <div class="hero-dots" id="heroDots"></div>
  <!--
    HERO IMAGE — the OMEN build, desk setup, or college machine.
    A dark shot with the silver/white hardware works best with the lighten blend.
    Path: images/pcbuilding/hero.jpg
  -->
  <div class="hero-img-wrap">
    <img src="images/pcbuilding/hero.jpg" alt="PC Build" onerror="this.style.display='none'">
  </div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="breadcrumb">
      <a href="projects.html">Projects</a><span>/</span><span>PC Building</span>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-tag">// REPAIR · REBUILD · UPGRADE · TWO MACHINES</div>
    <h1 class="hero-title">Fixing What's<br><span class="line2">Broken</span></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">
      It started with my grandmother's dead Dell XPS. One hard drive replacement, three case swaps,
      one custom OMEN build, and a college PC later — this is what learning hardware
      by actually doing it looks like.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-meta">
      <div class="meta-item"><span class="meta-label">Origin</span><span class="meta-value">2013 Dell XPS</span></div>
      <div class="meta-item"><span class="meta-label">Current Build</span><span class="meta-value">OMEN i7-13700K</span></div>
      <div class="meta-item"><span class="meta-label">Machines Running</span><span class="meta-value">2 Active</span></div>
      <div class="meta-item"><span class="meta-label">Next Up</span><span class="meta-value" style="color:#a78bfa">Friend's Upgrade</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="scroll-hint"><span>SCROLL</span><div class="scroll-arrow"></div></div>
</section>

<!-- MAIN -->
<main>

  <a class="back-link fade" href="projects.html">← Back to Projects</a>

  <!-- INTRO -->
  <div class="intro-block fade">
    <div>
      <span class="section-label">// HOW IT STARTED</span>
      <h2>A Dead Computer and a Curiosity About What Killed It</h2>
      <p>
        My grandmother's computer stopped working. The obvious move is to hand it to a
        repair shop and let someone else deal with it. Instead, I took it apart — not
        because I knew what I was doing, but because I wanted to understand what had
        actually gone wrong. That decision turned a written-off Dell XPS into a machine
        that's now keeping a friend through college, and turned a one-time curiosity
        into a skill I've been building ever since.
      </p>
      <p>
        What I've learned from all of this isn't just how to assemble components.
        It's how to <em>think about</em> a machine — what each part does, what failure
        looks like, what an upgrade actually changes versus what's just numbers on a
        spec sheet. That kind of knowledge only comes from opening the case.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-stack">
